# P2P Layer — Complete Rewrite Walkthrough

## Overview

Complete production rewrite of the P2P networking layer for 1M+ TPS. **9 files** rewritten, **~3,300 lines** of new code. Zero TODOs. Build and all tests pass.

---

## Files Changed

### Core Protocol

| File | Lines | Key Features |
|------|-------|-------------|
| [types.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/types.zig) | 275 | 20+ message codes, subnet bitmaps (64 subnets), participation bitmaps (256-bit), rate limit config, committee roles |
| [peer.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/peer.zig) | 310 | Stake-weighted rate limiting (token bucket with sqrt(stake) scaling), committee burst bonus, subnet tracking, reputation scoring with time-decay, auto-disconnect |
| [discovery.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/discovery.zig) | 430 | Full Kademlia (256 buckets × 16 nodes), XOR distance, subnet-aware peer search, ENR v4 serialization, bootstrap nodes, stale node eviction |

### Block & Transaction Propagation

| File | Lines | Key Features |
|------|-------|-------------|
| [turbine.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/turbine.zig) | 740 | GF(2^8) Reed-Solomon erasure coding with precomputed log/exp tables, Vandermonde encoding, Gaussian elimination decoding, adaptive shred count, stake-weighted propagation tree, shred collector with RS recovery |
| [gulf_stream.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/gulf_stream.zig) | 375 | Batch size 4096, deterministic leader prediction via `Hash(epoch‖slot) mod committee`, 3-leader lookahead, per-slot throttling (50 MB/slot), batch expiry (2 slots), queue depth management |
| [compression.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/compression.zig) | 390 | LZ4-style fast compression, ZCMP/ZRAW magic headers, raw fallback for incompressible data, 256 MB decompression cap, zero-heap-pressure hash table |

### Server & Module

| File | Lines | Key Features |
|------|-------|-------------|
| [server.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/server.zig) | 1,010 | 64 attestation subnets, committee-aware routing (shreds→tree, attestations→subnet, QC→committee, slash→all), stake-weighted rate limiting with committee burst, connection budget (max 512), batch I/O via sendmmsg, background peer pruning, configurable `ServerConfig`, handlers for all 20+ message types |
| [mod.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/mod.zig) | 35 | Clean module exports for all subsystems |
| [tests.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/tests.zig) | 595 | 35+ unit tests covering subnet bitmaps, participation counting, compression roundtrip, Reed-Solomon encode/decode/recovery, propagation tree, Kademlia discovery, peer scoring/rate-limiting/committee, Gulf Stream batching/expiry |

